-- Blue Financial CEO Van Niekerk Quits, Chairman to Act as Interim Chief
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-08-02T06:32:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/blue-financial-ceo-van-niekerk-quits-chairman-to-act-as-interim-chief.html

          
          
             Blue Financial Services Ltd. said
Chief Executive Officer Dave van Niekerk quit and that Chairman
Sipho Twala will act as interim-CEO.  
          
          


  


        